OL,3,CScaffolder speaks out about 'life-
OL,4,Cchanging' accident at power station
OL,6,FA scaffolder who became trapped under
OL,7,Fa two-tonne weight in an industrial
OL,8,Faccident has spoken about his life-
OL,9,Fchanging injuries.
OL,11,FColin Dell, 62, had to have toes
OL,12,Famputated after the accident at
OL,13,FDungeness B nuclear power station in
OL,14,F2022.
OL,16,FMr Dell, from New Romney in Kent, was
OL,17,Fworking near the main cooling water
OL,18,Fvalves when a two-tonne unsupported
OL,19,Fcounterweight fell on his foot.
