OL,3,CScaffolder speaks out about 'life-
OL,4,Cchanging' accident at power station
OL,6,F"I got diagnosed with severe PTSD and
OL,7,Fhad counselling for that. And I still
OL,8,Fhave to do grounding techniques every
OL,9,Fmorning just to get into work."
OL,11,F"It's changed my life completely."
OL,13,FFollowing the accident, EDF and
OL,14,FTrillium Flow Services Ltd have been
OL,15,Ffined a combined total of #633,333
OL,16,Fafter a prosecution prepared by the
OL,17,FOffice for Nuclear Regulation.
