OL,3,CScaffolder speaks out about 'life-
OL,4,Cchanging' accident at power station
OL,6,FThey pled guilty for failing to ensure
OL,7,Fthe safety of workers, in relation to
OL,8,Fthe risks arising whilst undertaking
OL,9,Fmaintenance and repair work.
OL,11,FThe investigation revealed a number of
OL,12,Fsignificant failings on the part of
OL,13,FEDF in the lead up to the accident and
OL,14,Fa lack of learning from a past similar
OL,15,Fincident at Dungeness B, in 2006.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
