OL,3,CScaffolder speaks out about 'life-
OL,4,Cchanging' accident at power station
OL,6,FThe regulator also discovered
OL,7,Fshortfalls in EDF's planning and
OL,8,Fresources, with employees being asked
OL,9,Fto fulfil roles outside of their
OL,10,Ftechnical capabilities and tasks being
OL,11,Fundertaken without the correct signed
OL,12,Fapprovals.
OL,14,FMeasures to reduce risks were not
OL,15,Ftaken and the company's health and
OL,16,Fsafety practices fell far below
OL,17,Fappropriate standards, ONR found.
OL,19,FSimilarly, the investigation also
OL,20,Ffound that Trillium Flow Services Ltd
OL,21,Fwere responsible for multiple failings.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
