OL,3,CScaffolder speaks out about 'life-
OL,4,Cchanging' accident at power station
OL,6,FThese included an unsuitable and
OL,7,Finsufficient risk assessment, a team
OL,8,Frelatively inexperienced in working on
OL,9,Fthe main counterweight valves at the
OL,10,Fsite, a lack of understanding of the
OL,11,Foperation of the valves and evidence
OL,12,Fof ill-informed decision-making.
OL,14,FDan Hasted, Director of Regulation at
OL,15,FOffice for Nuclear Regulation said:
OL,16,F"We welcome this outcome which
OL,17,Frecognises that EDF and Trillium Flow
OL,18,FServices Ltd failed in their duty to
OL,19,Fprotect a worker from a known risk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
