OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F417A1732118734
OL,3,CScaffolder speaks out about 'life-
OL,4,Cchanging' accident at power station
OL,6,F"This accident was wholly avoidable.
OL,7,FNobody should go to work and not come
OL,8,Fhome in a fit and healthy state.
OL,10,F"We conducted a thorough investigation
OL,11,Fwhich identified significant
OL,12,Fshortcomings by EDF and Trillium Flow
OL,13,FServices Ltd specifically their
OL,14,Ffailure to follow the correct sequence
OL,15,Ffor re-fitting the valve which
OL,16,Fresulted in the injuries to Mr Dell.
OL,18,F"We concluded that there were several
OL,19,Fmissed opportunities that could have
OL,20,Fprevented this accident occurring."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
