OL,6,FTrillium Flow Services didn't respond
OL,7,Ffor comment, but an EDF spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was an accident which
OL,9,Fshould never have occurred as safety
OL,10,Fis our over-riding priority.
OL,12,F"EDF today apologises to Mr Dell for
OL,13,Fits part in the injury caused and for
OL,14,Ffailing to meet our own rigorous
OL,15,Fsafety standards.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
