OL,3,CScaffolder speaks out about 'life-
OL,4,Cchanging' accident at power station
OL,6,F"The event serves as a reminder that
OL,7,Fwe must always be vigilant to any
OL,8,Frisks that could occur at our power
OL,9,Fstations. EDF has ensured the points
OL,10,Fhighlighted by the ONR have been fed
OL,11,Finto our processes at all of our sites
OL,12,Fand power stations to ensure everyone
OL,13,Fworking at all of our stations can
OL,14,Fwork safely."
OL,16,FDungeness B stopped generating power
OL,17,Fin June 2021 and is now in the
OL,18,Fdefueling stage.
